parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the motorized shoulder harness can cause the seat belt to malfunction, leading to inadequate restraint in the event of an accident, which can increase the risk of injury or fatality.
symptoms: The seat belt gets stuck in various positions
fails to retract
or locks in a closed position
requiring manual disengagement.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the automatic seat belt retractor can cause the seat belt to malfunction, leading to inadequate restraint in the event of an accident, which can increase the risk of injury or fatality.
symptoms: The seat belt retractor intermittently gets locked in a closed position
locking the driver or passenger in the vehicle
or fails to retract with the door.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the seat belt latch can cause the seat belt to malfunction, leading to inadequate restraint in the event of an accident, which can increase the risk of injury or fatality.
symptoms: The seat belt is unable to latch or becomes stuck
requiring manual intervention.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the rear seat belts can cause inadequate restraint in the event of an accident, which can increase the risk of injury or fatality.
symptoms: The rear seat belts fail to restrain occupants during an accident.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the driver's motorbelt can cause the seat belt to malfunction, leading to inadequate restraint in the event of an accident, which can increase the risk of injury or fatality.
symptoms: The driver's motorbelt fails.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: Transmission failure can cause the vehicle to lose power, stall, or become inoperable, leading to accidents or leaving the driver stranded. It can also cause the vehicle to roll back when in neutral, which can lead to accidents or injuries.
symptoms: Transmission jumps or slips out of gear
transmission lunges when shifting from a dead stop
transmission fails to engage into gear
transmission defaults to a higher gear when shifting from park to drive
vehicle becomes inoperable
engine revs but has no forward motion
transmission fluid leaks.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: Failure of the transmission electronic position switch can cause the transmission to malfunction, leading to accidents or leaving the driver stranded.
symptoms: Transmission defaults to a higher gear when shifting from park to drive
transmission fails to engage into gear
vehicle accelerates slowly from a standstill.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: Transmission fluid leaks can cause the transmission to malfunction or fail, leading to accidents or leaving the driver stranded.
symptoms: Transmission fluid leaks
transmission slips out of gear.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of engine mounts can cause vibrations, noise, and difficulty shifting gears, which can lead to a loss of control and accidents.
symptoms: Vibration under the hood
grinding noise
difficulty shifting gears
vehicle will not shift gears properly.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the muffler can cause excessive noise, decreased performance, and potentially lead to exhaust system damage.
symptoms: Muffler needs to be replaced multiple times.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: Engine overheating can cause damage to the engine, cooling system, and other components, leading to costly repairs and potentially leaving the driver stranded.
symptoms: Engine overheats.

parsedComplaintsResult.issueCategory: Door Handle Failure and Unexpected Door Opening
parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the door handle and the resulting unexpected door opening can cause injuries, accidents, or leave the driver and passengers vulnerable to theft or other safety risks.
symptoms: The door handle breaks
the door unexpectedly opens when lowering the window
the door opens from the outside
the rod falls inside the panel door
the door pops open when the window is down.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the rear gate assembly can cause injuries, accidents, or damage to the vehicle.
symptoms: The rear gate assembly falls off
the hatchback falls on the owner
causing injury.
